description:
The finale of Love is Blind: Season 10 is expected to release on Netflix on March 4, 2026.

This market will resolve according to the listed couples who are pronounced married by the end of the final episode of Love is Blind: Season 10. The reunion episode will not be taken into account. 

If the listed couple definitively splits or is otherwise not married by the end of the final episode of Love is Blind: Season 10, this market will resolve to "No".

If the season finale is not released or is definitively cancelled by June 30, 2026, 11:59PM ET, this market will resolve to "No couples marry".

The resolution source for this market will be the finale episode of Love is Blind: Season 10, or a consensus of credible reporting.
